Temporal bound
  [1, 12]

Evaluation
  128 x 128 x 12 trivariate lattice
  Density range: [0, 1.180061e-09]
```


:::
:::


### 6.8.5 Plotting the spatio-temporal KDE object


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
tims <- c(7,8,9,10,11,12)
par(mfcol=c(2,3))
for(i in tims){ 
  plot(st_kde, i, 
       override.par=FALSE, 
       fix.range=TRUE, 
       main=paste("KDE at month",i))
}
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](hands-on-exercise-3_1_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-12-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


## 6.9 Computing STKDE by Day of Year

### 6.9.1 Creating ppp object


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
fire_yday_ppp <- fire_sf %>% 
  select(DayofYear) %>%
  as.ppp()
```
:::


### 6.9.2 Including Owin Object


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
fire_yday_owin <- fire_yday_ppp[kbb_owin]
summary(fire_yday_owin)
